00:54:27.260 --> 00:54:30.310
When you draw somebody, it
registers in a different part

00:54:30.310 --> 00:54:32.280
of the brain, because you've
had the opportunity to

00:54:32.280 --> 00:54:34.560
evaluate their face,
break it down,

00:54:34.560 --> 00:54:36.280
work it into an equation.

00:54:36.280 --> 00:54:39.340
So actually, these guys I can
